html
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
  body(
    style='margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #fdfaf9; font-family: Arial, sans-serif'
  )
    include header.pug

    table(
      width='100%',
      cellpadding='0',
      cellspacing='0',
      border='0',
      style='padding: 20px 0'
    )
      tr
        td(align='center')
          table(
            width='600',
            cellpadding='0',
            cellspacing='0',
            border='0',
            style='border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; background-color: #ffffff'
          )
            // Greeting
            tr
              td(style='padding: 20px 30px 0 30px')
                p(
                  style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold'
                ) Hi #{ firstName },

            // Main intro
            tr
              td(style='padding: 20px 30px 0 30px')
                p(
                  style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold'
                ) Your week has been full of effort ‚Äî now‚Äôs your chance to capture the wins.
                p(style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 10px 0') Take 2‚Äì3 minutes to log what you accomplished this week. It doesn‚Äôt have to be perfect ‚Äî just honest.

            // Reflection purpose
            tr
              td(style='padding: 10px 30px 0 30px')
                p(
                  style='color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin: 10px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.5'
                )
                  | Reflection isn‚Äôt just about remembering what you did ‚Äî it helps you see how far you‚Äôve come and builds confidence for what‚Äôs next.

            // Weekly prompts
            tr
              td(style='padding: 15px 30px 0 30px')
                p(style='color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 5px 0') Need a spark? Try writing about:
                ul(
                  style='color: #555; font-size: 14px; padding-left: 20px; margin: 5px 0'
                )
                  li Something you solved or improved this week
                  li A moment you felt proud or recognized
                  li A skill you used or grew

            // üî• Streak section
            tr
              td(style='padding: 20px 30px 0 30px; text-align: center')
                if streakCount && streakCount > 0
                  p(
                    style='color: #333; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; font-weight: bold'
                  ) You're on a #{ streakCount }-week streak!
                  p(
                    style='color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin: 5px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.4'
                  ) Keeping this habit builds momentum ‚Äî each reflection makes your story stronger.
                else
                  p(
                    style='color: #333; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; font-weight: bold'
                  ) Start your reflection streak today!
                  p(
                    style='color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin: 5px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.4'
                  ) Each weekly reflection adds a chapter to your career story.

            // CTA button
            tr
              td(style='padding: 25px 30px 30px 30px; text-align: center')
                a(
                  href=weeklyLink,
                  style='background-color: #ff7a8a; color: #000000; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold'
                ) Add your achievements

            // Testimonial
            //- tr
            //-   td(style='padding: 20px 30px 0 30px')
            //-     blockquote(
            //-       style='margin: 20px 0; color: #666; font-style: italic; border-left: 4px solid #ff7a8a; padding-left: 10px'
            //-     )
            //-       | ‚ÄúWriting my weekly wins has made my performance reviews so much easier.‚Äù ‚Äì Career Fingerprint user

            // Tip footer
            tr
              td(style='padding: 10px 30px 20px 30px')
                p(
                  style='color: #777; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; margin-top: 10px'
                ) Tip: Add a quick Friday reminder to your calendar ‚Äî reflection only takes 3 minutes, but its impact lasts much longer.

    include footer.pug
